Package: KinaseDownstream
Type: Package
Title: Kinase downstream visualization
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-06-02
Author: Yuan Li
Maintainer: Who to complain to <yuan.li@nbis.se>
Description: This package provides functions to visualize the significantly enriched kinases in the phosphoproteomics data, the networks between each kinase, the downstream targets and their immediate String_db interacting neighbors that are observed from the matching proteomics data, facilitating the understanding of kinase interactions and their biological implications.
License: GPL-3
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    igraph,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    ggraph,
    STRINGdb,
    GSEABase,
    tibble,
    cmapR,
    ssGSEA2,
    xlsx,
    biomaRt,
    future,
    future.apply,
    BiocGenerics
